底，韓國大法院裁定，幾家日本公司須向二戰期間被日本強制勞役的韓國人另外進行賠償。<br />\n<br />\n日本政府認為韓國此舉破壞了兩國建交文件協議。</span></strong>但韓國法院認為，勞工受害者可以以反人類罪提起訴訟，向「與殖民統治直接有關的日本企業」索賠，而兩國協議中沒有涉及此類訴訟權利的規定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-49292261\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-49292261&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUioc%2FDYnbIFO1z8NzTSvCTwQ%3D&h=77ac60ad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-49292261&h=566bfe83\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-49292261</a>"},{"pid":"80d1b93ab788c0f149cd6c48d1e22b5d6874040a","tid":1518283,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T08:06:35.000Z","msg":"世界一直都好亂 只係之前唔關香港事 所以大家唔覺"},{"pid":"8722a5b134ea1c10a193e41b04d0fc047b165f85","tid":1518283,"uid":5258,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"60ed5d161c10cfad9b25b70e5fef4d23d610273b","tid":1518283,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b98b4a1df6f0f7eda778a9d3c0676b1fe613311b","tid":1518283,"uid":62321,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T08:03:35.000Z","msg":"俄佬好似自己地方核爆左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T08:05:23.000Z","msg":"俄佬(食緊花生) ：好彩我地咩事都冇啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T08:06:43.000Z","msg":"前排佢地唔係都示威咩<br />\n雖然唔算超級大單"},{"pid":"cfb15bfa3282caec17fa3593d7acee39d55c9807","tid":1518283,"uid":64757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T08:07:23.000Z","msg":"幾獲大單野   3 單同中共有關  你都咪話唔頭痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c59a1aa9f7a355989ddad1e7a54dd048054092d","tid":1518283,